    <div class="main review-item" id="7607038">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7607038/" class="title-link">一本超好看的中国近代史</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7607038"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/96989200/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u96989200-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/96989200/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">幽灵鱼</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2015-09-24"
      class="main-meta">2015-09-24 16:25:59</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7607038_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  权力，堪称悠悠五千年天下第一的绝世武尊。无坚不摧，战无不胜。所以几千年来，人们似乎在重复着同一种游戏——权力与利益的游戏。人人都希望自己成为游戏的最终获胜者。但他们不知道，在权力的游戏中，绝不会有永远的胜者。 

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/7607038/#comments">(6回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
